data.name: Engineering Document Management System
data.description: Developed a robust background processor and job scheduling system using .NET Core Azure Functions and Service Bus, improving document processing efficiency by 35%. Integrated SignalR for real-time notifications and used Fluent UI with React.js for a better user interface.

data.name: Revenue Lifecycle Management System
data.description: Developed unit test cases and packaged services as NuGet packages for microservices, improving system scalability and reliability. Built reusable services for better development efficiency.

data.name: India's First Scanner-Based Info for Monuments
data.description: Developed a scanner-based information system for monuments in Sambhajinagar, enabling smart access to historical data for the Aurangabad Mahanagar Palika (AMC Gov).
